product.title: Heys Disney Princess Kids Luggage
product.body_html:
Disney Princess Kids Luggage

Designed Especially for Kids. The ''Designer Disney' collection was created by Heys with the unique characteristics of children in mind, as it incorporates several design features that benefit children.

These beautiful cases have Disney characters specially printed onto their hardshell surfaces. There are a variety of unique character prints in this collection; these prints include popular Disney characters Princesses, Cars, Fairies, Minnie and Mickey Mouse, Doc. Mcstuffins, Sofia & Monsters Inc.

In creating a 'High-end' series for Disney, our designers incorporated several children-specific features. One of which, is the 'reverse-curve' handle system that curves the handle 'inwards & upwards' closer to the child, making it much more comfortable for the child - at a low height - to hold and navigate the case. The patent-pending design of this case also allows the wheels to 'protrude' out. This protrusion keeps the case elevated, so that even when being rolled at a very low height off the floor, the wheels will be the only point of contact and the case will continue to roll with ease. By weighing in at a mere 3.7 lbs, any child can wheel these fun cases around, as they also feature our inline skate wheels that make their rolling even better. It has a zipper closure system, that when opened reveals a beautifully lined interior with printed Disney patterns, as well as a zippered divider for internal organization. Comes with 2 Year Limited Warranty. Carry-on Approved. 18"x 11" x 9" ( 45.7 cm x 28cm x 23cm )
